\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"frontend服务出现大量HTTP 500错误和context canceled错误，表明前端服务因下游productcatalogservice超时而无法正常处理请求\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现分析：**\n\n1. **严重延迟问题**：frontend调用productcatalogservice的GetProduct操作，正常平均响应时间约11秒，但在故障时段飙升至56-60秒，延迟增加了约5000倍，这是极其显著的性能问题。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：从状态组合数据可见，故障传播路径为：\n   - productcatalogservice响应超时（rrt_max）\n   - frontend因等待超时出现context canceled错误\n   - 最终用户收到HTTP 500错误\n\n3. **根因定位**：根据拓扑关系，frontend->productcatalogservice是调用链中的关键路径。productcatalogservice作为被调用方出现严重延迟，是问题的根因，而frontend是受害者。\n\n4. **影响范围**：故障影响了所有frontend实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）和productcatalogservice实例，表明这是系统级别的性能问题。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "productcatalogservice is the root cause due to severe performance degradation causing RPC timeouts and context canceled errors"}
